content:
Add Excerpts to an Intent from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report

If you have an intent set, you can add excerpts directly from Einstein Conversation Mining.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience with the Service Intelligence add-on. 
Available in: Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Select a report, click on a topic summary name, select excerpts, then Add to Existing Intent.
Select your intent set and intent, save changes.
title: Adding Excerpts to Intents in Einstein Conversation Mining
